Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:50.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}包罗万象什么的 无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:52.33,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}脑袋里面加载
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.46,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是不是不可能的嘛
Comment: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.30,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:17.64,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直响着的沉默的警铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.86,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是谁的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.46,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳进去跳进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.82,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起来 破坏掉这无理的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:26.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不开这沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.41,0:03:28.83,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:31.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到终幕我都要说
